com.google.android.exoplayer.parser.webm

Class DefaultWebmExtractor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.android.exoplayer.parser.webm.DefaultWebmExtractor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    WebmExtractor

    public final class DefaultWebmExtractor
extends java.lang.Object
implements WebmExtractor
    Default version of an extractor to facilitate data retrieval from the WebM container format.

    WebM is a subset of the EBML elements defined for Matroska. More information about EBML and Matroska is available here. More info about WebM is here.
